{
  "name": "RPlog_A_New_Lightsaber",
  "title": "A New Lightsaber",
  "summary": "In the personal barracks of Talon Karrde's base on Myrkr, the dark Force-user Simon greets the ship captain Orson and the Jedi Jessalyn one early morning, and an awkward gathering forms as the mechanic Drew and a breakfast droid arrive. Simon quietly asks Orson to fly him, Jessalyn, and Mira when they soon leave Karrde's organization, and Orson agrees while Drew wrestles privately with where her own loyalties lie. Jessalyn then draws Simon into her room to show him the new lightsaber she built overnight while the Force-suppression field on Myrkr briefly lifted. Eager and playful, the two begin sparring -- her new blade against his energized rose-carved wooden staff -- until the suppression field abruptly returns mid-strike, the True Source vanishing just as Jessalyn's swing lands. Her saber cleaves Simon's staff and sears his chest. Horrified and unable to use the Force to heal him, Jessalyn tends his wound with a medkit, and the scene closes with Simon resting on her bed as she nurses him, the bond between them deepening through her guilt and his forgiveness.",
